<plot>Valslav works for a multinational corporation as a minor accountant; he hates his work and has a secret ambition to be a dancer - but his job forbids contact with artistic organizations. He finds Bird, an exotic hybrid woman who teaches dance to a bizarre community and has a pet wolf. Frame the corporate surveillance man and DOG the security guard follow Vaslav to the studio and film him dancing; they show the evidence to KASH the company boss who confronts Vaslav. Bird flies in....and somehow, with the help of wolf, the world is changed...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?570821</url></doc>
